<html>
<head>
<style type="text/css">
.vm-container {
	margin: 10px;
}
.vm-page-content {
	border: 1px solid #2a3f54;
	height: 150%;
	color: #000;
}

.vm-page-content .head {
	background-color: #2a3f54;
	padding: 10px;
	color: #FFFFFF;
}

.head .images {
	margin-left: 10px;
}

.vm-page-content .body {
	padding: 10px;
	font-size: 12px;
}
.resp{
margin: 5px 0px;
}
.resp h5 {
	font-size: 13px;
	font-weight: 600;
}

.body .cont p {
	margin: 0 0 8px;
	text-align: justify;
	line-height: 20px;
}

.sub-title {
	font-size: 13px;
	font-weight: 600;
	line-height: 30px;
}

.sub-mrg-content {
	margin-top: 3px;
	margin-bottom: 3px;
	padding-left: 30px;
}
.sub-mrg-content li{
line-height: 25px;
}
.btn{
padding: 10px;
background:  #2a3f54;
color: #ffffff;
margin: 5px;
text-align: center;
border-radius:3px;
}
.footer {
	padding: 10px;
	background: #fff;
}
.footer-reg{
font-size: 12px;
	color: #000;
	font-weight: 600;
	line-height: 20px;
}
.footer .quas {
	margin-top: 20px;
	font-size: 12px;
}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="vm-container">
	<div class="vm-page-content">
		<div class="head">
			<div class="images">
				<img src="cid:imagess"alt="MyJobKart"/>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="body">
			<div class="resp">
				<h5>Dear ${fname},</h5>
			</div>
			<div class="cont">
				<p>Thanks for registering with MyJobKart.com. Your account has been created successfully.</p>
				<p>Please click the below link for account activation. </p>
					<a href ="${url}${email}"><div class="btn" style="width:180px;">
					Activate Your Account</div>
					</a>
                    <p>Be an active member of MyJobKart.com by creating your profile.</p>
            <p>Profile creation enables the employer to utilize the below services offered, </p>        
                  <ul class="sub-mrg-content">
                  <li>Create Sub User profile- The employer can create a maximum of 10 sub users with the same accessibility that he/she has.</li>
                   <li>Post a Job- The employer/sub user can post a job with the listed mandatory fields.</li> 
                    <li>Post a walk in- The employer/sub user can post a walk in job.</li>
                    <li>Find Candidate- The employer/sub user can search for a suitable candidate in accordance with the fields like Job Title, key skills and so on.</li>
                    <li>Save Candidate- The employer/sub user can save a candidate for short listing or saving it for future reference.</li>
                    <li>Applied Candidate- The employer/sub user can shortlist the eligible candidate.</li>
                    <li>Upload Job Posts- The employer/sub user can upload bulk jobs.</li>
                    </ul>
                       
				<div class="sub-title">Special Services :</div>
				<ul class="sub-mrg-content">
					<li>Initial trial package for an employer is 10 days and thereon the employer has to opt for our special services to maximize their efficacy in recruiting a suitable candidate.</li>
					<li>Your Special Services has been segregated in " VIBGYOR" manner, scaling from Violet to Red; please visit our product page to get elaborated information on the same.</li>
					
				</ul>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="footer">
        <div class="footer-reg">
        Your Search for a mine ends here.</div>
			<div class="footer-reg">
				Warm Regards<br /> MyJobKart.com
			</div>
			<div class="quas">
				For more clarifications, ping us at  <b>info@myjobkart.com</b>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
</body></html>
